attributes.Long form description: The student grabs the allen wrench and starts to unscrew the top table of the furniture. Then, he continues to unscrew the first leg of the furniture and put all the screws on the table. After that, he rotates the furniture and unscrews the second leg. He rotates the furniture again and it seems that he is going to unscrew the third leg but he regrets it and lays down the furniture and detaches the first leg. Then he detaches the second leg and rotates the furniture. The student starts to unscrew the third leg and then he detaches it. He grabs the third leg and put it on the table. After that, the student rotates the furniture and unscrews the fourth leg, and detaches the top table from it. The student holds the fourth leg and keeps unscrewing it but by mistake, he drops the allen wrench. The student grabs again the allen wrench and continues unscrewing the fourth leg. He detaches the fourth leg from the shelf and put all the pieces on the table.

attributes.Transcription: We'll go now to disassemble the table from IKEA.
So please go ahead and disassemble it.
